				h6 Technologies
				p FigJam, Figma, Wordpress, Elementor, HTML, PHP, SCSS, JS, ACF

/! Portfolio Details
section.portfolio-info#info
	.container-fluid.px-md-0
		.row.justify-content-between.g-0.mx-md-0
			.summary.col-12.col-md-5.position-sticky.d-flex.align-items-center.vh-100.mx-auto.top-0.px-lg-5
				.flex-grow-1.py-8.py-md-10
					h2 Project Details
					h6
						span.badge.text-bg-secondary Problem
					p Firmatek’s existing website no longer reflected their evolving brand or the sophistication of their data solutions. It needed a clearer content structure and a refreshed visual system to better represent Firmatek's growing capabilities.
					h6
						span.badge.text-bg-secondary Process
					p I led the redesign from strategy to development, starting with a refined sitemap and content structure. I designed wireframes and high-fidelity mockups using Firmatek’s updated brand system, then built a custom WordPress theme with modular, reusable blocks. The entire process focused on improving usability, strengthening brand cohesion, and presenting Firmatek’s technical expertise in a clear, user-friendly way.
					h6
						span.badge.text-bg-secondary Outcome
					p The new website is modern, responsive, and strategically structured to guide users through Firmatek’s solutions. The redesign provides Firmatek with a scalable digital foundation that supports ongoing growth and enhances their credibility as an industry leader.
					/ p The redesign provides Firmatek with a scalable digital foundation that supports ongoing growth and enhances their credibility as an industry leader.
